===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

The original character is [[&#64096;]]. {{Han compound|衣|alt1=⻂|曷|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=clothing}}. It conveys the meaning "a garment made of coarse cloth," and by extension, "rough or shabby clothing." The modern Jōyō kanji is a simplified form.<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

